00:00:15.000 --> 00:01:27.000
In a medium bowl mix eggs and sugar

00:01:27.000 --> 00:01:57.000
Add flour, butter and milk! The batter must be smooth

00:01:57.000 --> 00:02:08.000
Add backing powder

00:02:08.000 --> 00:02:40.000
Divide the batter in 2 bowls and cocoa in 1 of these

00:02:40.000 --> 00:02:51.000
If the cocoa batter is not very smooth ,you 
 can add a little more of milk

00:02:51.000 --> 00:04:12.070
Then grease a circular or a rectangular pan and pour alternately 
 the “white” batter and the cocoa one in it.

